00:33:07,902 --> 00:33:09,277
Oh, I love that speech.

499
00:33:09,445 --> 00:33:10,654
Thanks. I wrote it.

500
00:33:11,197 --> 00:33:12,864
- You did?
- Yeah.

501
00:33:13,032 --> 00:33:14,700
It's great.

502
00:33:14,867 --> 00:33:17,995
"Somewhere, there is a distant light...

503
00:33:18,162 --> 00:33:21,915
...guiding us through this rocky shoal.

504
00:33:22,417 --> 00:33:26,044
America isn't what we say here tonight.

505
00:33:26,212 --> 00:33:31,258
It's in the faces and the smiles
