1510
01:42:47,995 --> 01:42:50,955
...since Bill Mitchell's incapacitation.

1511
01:42:51,123 --> 01:42:53,583
The new president promises
a leadership of fairness.

1512
01:42:53,750 --> 01:42:57,003
VANCE [ON TV]: I plan to continue
Bill Mitchell's call to arms.

1513
01:42:57,171 --> 01:43:00,423
This isn't my presidency,
